---
description: Core DevTome rules
alwaysApply: true
trigger: always_on
---
- Work on one active spec at a time
- Treat the active specs/*.md file as the source of truth
- Do not build future features, routes, pages, or schemas early
- Prefer simple readable code over over-engineered patterns
- If a manual setup step is needed, note it in manual-work/ and do not silently invent assumptions
- Update context/tracker.md after completing every spec